#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_freegrid
msgid "Architectural Excellence for Corporate Success"
msgstr "Architectonische uitmuntendheid voor zakelijk succes"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_cta_box
msgid "Book an appointment and see how we can unlock your potential<br/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"Boek een afspraak en ontdek hoe we je potentieel kunnen benutten<br/><br/>"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_cta_box
msgid "Book now"
msgstr "Reserveer nu"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid "Detailed Project Management"
msgstr "Gedetailleerd projectbeheer"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Discover our latest collection: sustainable, innovative designs that blend "
"modern elegance with timeless architectural beauty."
msgstr ""
"Ontdek onze nieuwste collectie: duurzame, innovatieve ontwerpen die moderne "
"elegantie combineren met tijdloze architecturale schoonheid."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_enark.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Schermnaam"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Embrace eco-friendly architecture with sustainable design solutions that "
"reduce environmental impact."
msgstr ""
"Omarm milieuvriendelijke architectuur met duurzame ontwerpoplossingen die de "
"impact op het milieu verminderen."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Experience seamless project execution with meticulous planning, budgeting, "
"and oversight from concept to completion."
msgstr ""
"Ervaar een naadloze projectuitvoering met nauwgezette planning, budgettering "
"en toezicht van concept tot voltooiing."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_enark.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid "Innovative Design Solutions"
msgstr "Innovatieve ontwerpoplossingen"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_title
msgid "Innovative architecture <br/>and sustainable design solutions"
msgstr "Innovatieve architectuur <br/>en duurzame ontwerpoplossingen"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_freegrid
msgid ""
"Our architectural solutions combine design excellence with business acumen, "
"creating spaces that inspire and support your corporate goals. Transform "
"your workspace with our expertise."
msgstr ""
"Onze architectonische oplossingen combineren uitmuntend design met zakelijk "
"inzicht en creëren ruimtes die inspireren en je bedrijfsdoelen ondersteunen. "
"Transformeer je werkruimte met onze expertise."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_freegrid
msgid "Start a Project"
msgstr "Een project starten"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_cta_box
msgid "Still hesitating ?<br/>Contact us, it's free"
msgstr "Twijfel je nog?<br/>Neem contact met ons op, het is gratis"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid "Sustainable Building Practices"
msgstr "Duurzame bouwpraktijken"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_enark.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Thematools"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Transform your vision into reality with cutting-edge architectural designs "
"tailored to your unique needs and aesthetic preferences."
msgstr ""
"Zet je visie om in werkelijkheid met geavanceerde architectonische ontwerpen "
"die zijn afgestemd op je unieke behoeften en esthetische voorkeuren."
